# National Register of Historic Places listings in Muskingum County, Ohio

__NOTOC__
This is a list of the National Register of Historic Places listings in Muskingum County, Ohio.
This is intended to be a complete list of the properties and districts on the National Register of Historic Places in Muskingum County, Ohio, United States. Latitude and longitude coordinates are provided for many National Register properties and districts; these locations may be seen together in an online map.
There are 84 properties and districts listed on the National Register in the county.  Another 5 properties were once listed but have been removed.
